@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.13/js/solid.js" integrity="sha384-tzzSw1/Vo+0N5UhStP3bvwWPq+uvzCMfrN1fEFe+xBmv1C/AtVX5K0uZtmcHitFZ" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.13/js/fontawesome.js" integrity="sha384-6OIrr52G08NpOFSZdxxz1xdNSndlD4vdcf/q2myIUVO0VsqaGHJsB0RaBE01VTOY" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Dancing+Script:700|Open+Sans|Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/Content/Index.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/Content/Carousel.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/Content/style3.css" rel="stylesheet" />


</head>
<body>
    <!--===========carousel========-->
    <div>
        <div id="mycarousel" class="carousel slide carousel-fade hoverable" data-interval="3000" data-ride="carousel">
            <!-- Indicators -->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>

            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="carouselImage" src="../Content/Images/restaurants.jpg" style="width:100%; height: 100%;" />

                    <div class="container" id="captionContainer1">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h2>Order Food From </h2>
                            <h1>Restaurants</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="carouselImage" src="../Content/Images/homemadefood.jpg" style="width:100%" />


                    <div class="container" id="captionContainer2">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h2>Order Food From </h2>
                            <h1 id="GlowText">Home Chefs</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="carouselImage" src="../Content/Images/recipes.jpg" style="width:100%" />

                    <div class="container" id="captionContainer3">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h2 id="whiteH">Write Your </h2>
                            <h1 id="white">Recipes</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="carouselImage" src="../Content/Images/food_blog.jpg" style="width:100%" />


                    <div class="container" id="captionContainer4">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h2>Start Writting</h2>
                            <h1 id="foodBlogH1">Food Blogs</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#mycarousel" data-slide="prev"><span id="carouselButton" class="fas fa-chevron-left"></span></a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#mycarousel" data-slide="next"><span id="carouselButton" class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></a>

        </div>

        <!--===========Welcome Doc&Dine========-->

        <section class="welcome-area section-padding2">
            <div class="container-fluid" id="welcomeArea">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                        <div class="welcome-img">
                            <img src="~/Content/Images/welcome-bg.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                        <div class="welcome-text mt-5 mt-md-0">
                            <h3>
                                <span class="style-change">Welcome</span> <br>to
                                <img src="~/Content/Images/logo1.png" style="width:300px;height:100px;">
                            </h3>
                            <p class="pt-3">Bangladeshis are always renowned as a food loving nation. Our country has an enriched culture of different type of cuisine. So we are here to bring all the food lovers together.</p>
                            <p>With our platform we will meet your demands be it food recipes, food blogging or to order food at home or from restaurants.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="template-btn mt-3">book a table</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!--===========Homefood & Recipe========-->
        <section class="pb_md_py_cover text-center cover-bg-black cover-bg-opacity-4" style="background-image: url(../../Content/Images/mid-bg11.jpg);opacity:0.9;" id="section-home">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-md-9  order-md-1">
                        <h2 class="heading mb-3">Delicious &amp; Nutritious</h2>
                        <p class="sub-heading">Bored from restaurant foods? Join here to order homemade foods and discover recipes to get the nutritious food in your menu</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!--==========================Offer================================-->

        <section class="bg-lightGray section-padding">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row no-gutters">
                    <div class="col-sm">
                        <img class="card-img rounded-0" src="../Content/Images/pizza1.jpg" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm">
                        <div class="offer-card offer-card-position">
                            <h4 style="font-family:'Pacifico', cursive;">-Deal of the day-</h4>
                            <h3>Italian Pizza Offer</h3>
                            <h2>50% OFF</h2>
                            <a class="button" href="#">Get Premium Membership</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <!--===========restaurant reservation========-->
        <section class="reservation">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-6">
                    <div class="signn">
                        <h1>Reservation</h1>
                        
                            <form action="Reserve" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="Name">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group col-md-12 ">
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="Email Address">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="phn" placeholder="Phone Number">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="resName" placeholder="Restaurant Name">
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                                    <select class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                                        <option>No of people</option>
                                        <option>1</option>
                                        <option>2</option>
                                        <option>3</option>
                                        <option>4</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
 
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-danger text-uppercase">Make Reservation</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!--===========blogger========-->

        <div class="blogger_index">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-6">

                    <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/Images/chef1.jpg" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <h1>Simple Sweet and Sour Sauce</h1>
                    <p>
                        One of my biggest pet peeves is having a million half-used condiments in my fridge. So if I can quickly whip up a homemade sauce with pantry staples, I’m going to do that before buying another bottle! This Simple Sweet and Sour Sauce is the perfect example. At its most basic, a sweet and sour sauce is just sugar and vinegar, flavored with a splash of soy sauce and ketchup. But there are also plenty of ways you can jazz it up and make it your own, so I’ll also include those below!
                    </p>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-danger text-uppercase">Read Blogs</button>
                </div>



            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
